chipDescription: A heavy and hard orb. It is in fact the key to Gensokyo.
expressions: Rhythm? Isn't it all about defeating the enemies?
Buro? That kid is kinda like Suika ... Noisy, but not annoying.
Have nothing to do, huh? Would you like a cup of tea?
Ughhh Yukari! Got tricked by her prank again and now I'm here!
Enough already, I did my part didn't I?
Do you ever get tired of poking me? You know that I'm not ticklish, right?
Props? Illustrations? Is there nothing more valuable?
You're welcome, please put my pay in the donation box~
I have made up my mind, how about building a shrine here too? This will double my income!
For what you've done to me, I will take double the payback!
Why are you so concerned about my armpits? There is no weak point here!
Want an S? That will cost you 100,000 yen. No? Then what?

skill: Clear can automatically catch all the missed Blue Notes, Red Hearts, ghosts, and enemies with Heart. The automatically caught ghosts and enemies with Heart is "Perfect" judgment.
chipDescription: The crown which brings Clear falling to the ground, absolutely who hit by it will shout Ouch.
expressions: Born in the grave, standing for the return of glory! How about it, isn't it cool?
Fail comes here with me? What a clingy girl... Don't worry, I'll take care of her myself!
Clear will clear all the songs here! Eh... an awkward silence?
How long are you going to cool my heels? Hurry up and start playing with me! Come on, come on, come on!
Love from everyone is the source of my power, so always praise me~
Today is the day of solo with Fail, whoever loses will do whatever the winner says! Come and cheer me on!
Is that little zombie named Buro also resurrected from the graveyard? What...that is a cosplay?!
You want me to fight with the guitar... What if I destroy it? I mean the mob of monsters!
Just now! I saved another spectator who was almost bewitched by Fail. It was literally a close call.
I don't look like Fail. Obviously I'm in better shape... Yes, that's definitely true!
Eh? Eh? Ah... I can't take it anymore! If you want something, just say it!
Ahhhh, geez! To prevent you from poking me and thus losing the game, keep three meters away from now on!

skill: Sister Marija will swap the locations of enemies in the sky and on the ground. Specifically, raiders, hanging hammers, and ordinary obstacles (gears) will be rolled over.
chipDescription: She finds the star shape more adorable for it’s a symbol of her belief.
expressions: A good sense of smell, careful planning, and swift handling—those are what I've learned at the Church.
Can enemies be defeated by prayers only? Of course not. So let's get started, while God is still in slumber.
You need not fear me. Only bad people are my target... Huh, are you here to confess?
Enemies? It-It is they that targeted me first. I just... beat them too hard...
If you are really a kind-hearted person, you should support me, as long as the result is correct, no...?
Even if you are against my approach, we are already accomplices... So what do you think should be done to traitors...
Unlike my devil who has a gentle soul, my angel is a naughty kid... Well, keep it a secret to the Church.
Wanna make a confession? Just tell me about it. I'm efficient~
Familiars, who have lived several hundreds of years, can even argue about either the bunny girl suit or the sailor suit is cuter for a whole day. Oh, this is really...
Behave yourself... This is not any doctrine, but something that even a child can understand...
Calm down, calm down, Marija... Don't submit to profane temptations. Come recite prayers. That's right, that's what you should do...
What a sinful person... you are. I really look forward to the day when you are punished by myself...

skill: Marisa can keep hovering in the air without automatically landing. She gains a 200% score bonus when catching Blue Notes or Red Hearts in full health.
chipDescription: A mighty self-made magical item that can shoot lasers when stuffed with mushrooms - use it to blast your way to Gensokyo!
expressions: I am the Great Magician—Kirisame Marisa! … Huh? You didn’t think it was me?
Not like someone, if your request brings me fun, I won't charge you ~ ☆
Treating every enemy with care is not my style. Let me teach you how to use Master Spark ~ ☆
It's Marija's book, I borrowed it! ...Taking a book can't be considered stealing!
The mushroom world is really complicated! It took me a night to do a little research! So—please don't look at me as if I were an overachiever.
My luck today is… future blessing?! Future blessing again? Isn't it  "Almost Misfortune "!!
Ah~ There are too many notes in some stages. Now, I understand how they feel when they see my danmaku…
Don't give me that"please do Love Sign Master Spark again"look! I'm not a busking magician!
I was called by a dangerous-looking girl in black to dust her car… Do I look like a maid?
What are you staring at?! Ah… How do you know there are bombs under my dress?
You can't eat that mushroom! It is… the magic mushroom, which can increase intimacy between you and who you love… I don't know the details! I didn't eat it!!
Stop—I handed over everything I stole... I took!If you dare do something that crosses the line, I'll call Reimu to sort you out!

skill: Amiya earns more Fever Energy by repelling enemies. When Fever Mode is active, she will convert "Miss" into "Great", and "Great" into "Perfect". However, Amiya will not earn any Fever Energy for 3 seconds after Fever Mode ends.
chipDescription: One of Amiya's ten rings. Not sure which finger it's for, but it definitely won't fit you, Doctor.
expressions: The very thought of performing before you is making me a little nervous, Doctor... but I'll do my best!
Running with music makes it easier. I must share this discovery with Miss Dobermann. It'll be great if she uses this in training!
There are still many stages to challenge, Doctor... but make sure you get some rest, okay?
Do the enemies feel pain if I knock them back with my Originium Arts? What? They enjoy this...? Alright then.
Perhaps you can try mashing the buttons to get through the enemy mob. Don't give up now, Doctor.
Swing that violin like a weapon? If I must...
Strategy matters, even in rhythm games. Let's have a mission briefing, Doctor.
I just plucked up my courage to ask Miss Marija for some violin tips, but she just picked me up and spun me around and around... Was that a yes or no?
Please predict the charts based on our intel about the boss, Doctor! What? You can't? I'm sorry.
My violin skills have improved? Thank you, Doctor... you're also getting better at the game.
I'm so happy to hear people around us say how reliable you are, Doctor. But does that mean you're secretly doing overtime? I thought you told me you were getting some rest...
Me? No, I'm not nervous... but getting stage fright is pretty normal, Doctor. Do let me know if you're nervous as well.

skill: Ola will not get hurt when bursting into Fever. But in exchange for the temporary command, he can only use Sis's skill? His rebellion is totally frustrated!
chipDescription: A mountain of champion belts at home? How about we take them to Sis and transform them into henshin device?!
expressions: I just found out I only have Sis's skill... Um, maybe it's okay. She is powerful after all...
Ahhhhh, I'm so nervous. Think back to what Sis once told me: "Run away from the fight you can't win."Run away from the fight I can't win. Run away from the fight I can't win...
Wow, I'm really weak in human form. I have a bad feeling that I'm gonna make a fool of myself... Oh, no...
Gloves, check. Headgear, check. Henshin device, check. Skill, check. Good! I'm invincible today!!
Ola ola ola ola ola! My endless punches can defeat any enemy!!
This is my trump card, Bear Punch! If that's not enough, Bear Punch Plus! Still not enough? Bear Punch Ultimate!
Stamina—As long as I have it, I can take care of all my enemies! You should get more exercise like me, partner!
Bear, sanjou! How about that? I'm a copycat? It’s not that obvious!
Sis is in that bear in pink braces? It can't be! Wait a minute, let me look again...?
Feel lonely because sisters are not here? Me, too. But I can play with you like sisters did... Maybe?
I used to feel your gaze when I was in bear form...
But now I don't have the soft, furry tummy. So... that means... you have nothing to feel, do you?

skill: Exorcist Master Buro will first consume Fever Energy every time she gets hurt. When Fever Mode is active, defeating enemies grants 30% bonus scores.
chipDescription:
The switch to turn on the streamer's serious mode, 
with cracks indicating the end of it.
expressions: No matter it's the Eastern monster or the Western demon, there's nothing I can't exorcise. Alas, it's getting harder to scrape a living~
Tit for tat is fair game! If you invite something like a zombie or demon, don't count on me to rescue you~
Distressed everyday, how unlucky you are. But that's why you are a perfect match for someone like me, a 24/7 genius Exorcist Master~
Ola, you might notice it too—this place must be haunted by an evil spirit!
That suspicious sister does business but collects no money. I smelled something fishy! Let me check her out!
I saw you surrounded by darkness. This must be... Er, sorry, I forgot to take off the sunglasses!
Is the streamer blind—this is my important prop to show... exorcise the demons!! I'll kill you!!
Snacks were gone? Figures were broken? I said it a thousand times! Spoiled brats are not ghosts! Fix it yourself!
Something is moving behind the streamer? Please raise your head and take a good look at the stream title? You can't even fool the ghosts!
How about sealing... your head filled with evil thoughts?
When you have sleep paralysis, just imagine it's Buro sitting on you... Please hang in there a little longer!
Sleeping with the pillow consecrated by me can bring you a good fortune... How about that? Wanna buy it?

skill: Hatsune Miku can hit enemies and Sheets(hold note) regardless of the upper and lower tracks. But this skill doesn't work on the Blue Notes, Red Hearts, and barriers.
chipDescription: It has the power to convey the singing to the whole universe, but there's also a possibility that it will be thrown to the audience as a bunch of leeks?
expressions:
Be it a 2- or 24-hour concert, 
just leave it to me!

This new suit looks so cute, 
doesn't it? Look at this Muse-bag... 
It tells me what the next song is!

I'll take part in Buro's Gourmet 
and Music Festival as a representative of Team Leek
—there's no such team?!

I'm so glad to hear that 
my live performance stopped troublemaking monsters from fighting~

I can feel your passion 
for music while watching you challenge the stage again and again... 
I have the same feelings as you!

Here I encountered you, 
found new songs, and made new friends... 
I have gained so much!

I just forgot what I wanted to say after I opened my mouth.
 Maybe I can remember it after a meal. 
Okay, let's eat something—

During my live performance, 
a flying cat threw me a fish. 
Is that a gift for me?

A ghost came to me for a photo. 
It looked so happy despite the fact that 
there's only me in it...
Let me convey the words in your heart by singing...

Luka-san is so attractive on stage. 
When I met her eyes, 
her wink almost made me forget the lyrics...

Let me perform your favorite song! Why?
 Because I want to know more about... you.

skill: Kagamine Rin & Len can 100% earn you a "Perfect" judgement when you hit the enemies that reach the hitboxes at the same time on both tracks. If you only hit the enemy on one track, they can help you auto-hit the enemy on the other. But this skill doesn't work on Sheets (hold note), Mash Enemies and BOSS' melee attacks.
chipDescription: Just like this pair of G and F clefs, they have the confidence to work in tune at any instance!
expressions: Did you call me? If you want to praise me, don't hesitate to do it~
If I turn into a bear... I'll make my audience jump out of their skin! Let Len try it out next time!
Forget my lyrics? Don't worry, my freestyle will be the best solution!
Did you call me? If you need any help, don't hesitate to say it!
I'm making the special strategy to confront Luka-san. No peeking at it before I finish it!
Right... I also memorized Rin's lyrics—the show is gonna be 100% foolproof～
Prank Time! Let's go scare Miku-san～<=>It seems this unintended prank scared me first.
Verification Time! Len can make a knee-jerk reaction to our songs no matter which second they start from and dance with it, can't you?<=>You just wanna play that kind of game, don't you?
Quiz Time! What is Len thinking now?<=>You'd never know. Bring it on!
I will find you from the stage, don't you look around!<=>She means please keep your eyes on us!
It's a little bit weird to have new clothes on. I can't help but look in the mirror...<=>She means she really likes the new clothes, and me too!

There is a bewildering variety of songs...
 Good, we can show our charms in all aspects!<=>That means... We really had fun, thank you!

skill: When Racer Rin's HP is above 150, the "Miss" judgment on the same track with the character can be converted into "Great". Rin still gets hurt by that enemy, but the invincible time after the injury can increase by 1 second; When its HP is below 150, the "Great" judgment can be converted into "Perfect", but there's no additional invincible time. This skill doesn't work on Sheets (hold note) or Mash Enemies.
chipDescription: Not only hides her murderous eyes but also highlights her cute wolf ears. Follower+1!
expressions: The wind has risen... Where do you wanna go today?
Tires, chains, and the clutch all have to be renewed. Today is a great day for working hard in the factory~

You can't see the back of your head, right? And the werewolf itself doesn't know what it looks like after the transformation... But I'm quite sure that I must be a fierce one. You should be careful of that~
This is not the cat ear, and that is not the dog tail. Wolf, have you heard of the wolf?
That fake exorcist master comes to trouble me again. Come on, the werewolf transformation has totally nothing to do with the spirit possession...
The bonus should definitely be used to modify my motorcycle... Uhm, my pocket is empty again. When will the next race be held?
One, two, three, four... No more at all? Someone who I can surpass.
The street is wet from the rain. That girl in black moves quite fast. I'll catch her up.
When I'm fast, the moon is close; when I'm slow, the moon is far.
Let me tell you how to comb my hair. From the ear to the tail... Take it slow and be gentler. That's right.
If I fix you greatly... You can behave better than this motorcycle, can't you?
The injury on your neck... was caused by my bite? To be honest, I don't want to take responsibility for something that I don't even remember~

skill: Mechanical Ballerina Marija will automatically receive Fever Energy over time. The higher the difficulty of the stage, the quicker the speed of Fever Energy accumulation. However, Marija will receive no Fever Energy when she repels the enemy.
chipDescription: An android pets a robot cat. Anything wrong?
expressions: Rome wasn't built in a day. Behind every dance performance are thousands of code tests.
Build the stage? I can do it all alone. For the android, it's just like blowing off dust.
My movements are quite agile? Thanks, I only hit where it hurts.
Get some rest... How long does "some" mean?
All my targets were reached. Please set new targets for me.
I tried to add singing to the performance, but the audience accused me of lip-synching... Is it because my singing sounds exactly like the studio version?
The Doctor is my lifesaver? No, I don't think an android will feel gratitude just because it hasn't been scrapped...
That mad scientist who's sitting on the UFO is the Doctor who modified me. She only creates pointless inventions.
That doll made for the Doctor melted under the scorching sun. Cotton candy is not the candy made of the cotton, but the cotton made of the candy...
Humans show affection by adopting a close interpersonal distance. I see. But if it's getting too close, my cooling system may be out of order...
I'm replaying your gaming clip. Don't worry, I didn't edit your score... Need I?
It takes me more time to handle compliments than orders... Please wait a moment.
autoExpressions: Every time I meet with the Doctor, she adds some useless functions to me, such as the sweating simulator which leads to not only a waste of memory but also a short circuit. It may make me look like a human, but that doesn't mean I can become one.
